      "date": "2013-01-30 17:16:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nAs per http://review.whamcloud.com/3955 it is not possible to be able to put this content into a Macro. \n\nLooks good to me.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
