      "date": "2013-01-30 18:10:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/52959742-6b08-11e2-aa62-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
