        "username": "sebastien.buisson",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-01-31 09:24:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYou are right Bob, there are so many similar calls in the code. Sometimes Coverity correctly resolves the function pointer, and sometimes it fails to, which leads to a false positive error.\nAdding the necessary comments proactively is a huge task from my point of view.",
